data.description: This lovely, 3BD/2BA, 1317 SF home is perfect for anyone looking for a cozy and well-maintained space just outside of Ardmore. Laminate flooring in the main living areas adds a touch of sophistication, with carpet in the master bedroom for added comfort.   With ceiling fans in almost every room, this home offers comfort and energy efficiency in every season. The nice-sized yard is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening outdoors. The concrete driveway and two-car attached garage provide ample parking and storage space for all your needs.  Outside, you'll find a wooden deck, fenced yard, and storage building, adding versatility and convenience to this charming property.
